  A-eng in2-khi2 chiong2-chiong2 hong-hong u2-u2, Siu3-tin tit8-tit8 lun2 boe7 tiau5, koh m7-chai beh an2-choaN2 ka7 A-eng khng3-kai2, tioh8 kin2 tau5 hou7 Jit8-seng thiaN! ¡§Hong-siaN pong3-iaN2--a, bo5-iaN2 bo5 ji7-jiah e5 tai7-chi3, li2 ia7 teh sin3 kah hit-peng5 khi3.¡¨ Jit8-seng thiaN Siu3-tin kong2 boe7 soah to7 ka7 pok-tiau7: ¡§Io lam2--leh ia7 ho2, chhiu2 khan-chhiu2 teh chhit-tho5 ia7 ho2, lan2 A-eng chiah boe7 piN3 he gin2-a2-chhut--leh, li2 bian2 thiaN A-hoe teh hoe7.¡¨ ¡§Ah bo5, iau2 u7 siaN2 toa7-lang5-chhut? Li2 kong2 lai5 thiaN khoaN3-mai7--leh.¡¨ Siu3-tin kong2 bo5 kui2 ku3, hou7 pok-tiau7 chiaN5 put-hok8: ¡§Goa2 si7 kiaN i...kiaN i...hou7 lang5 sian3-tong7--khi3.¡¨ ¡§A-eng beh hou7 lang5 sian3-tong7 e7 khi3 oh? He chin piaN3--leh! Li2 bo5 khoaN3 chit kui2 ni5 cho3 seng-li2 cheng kah na2 siaN2, li2 bian2 chhau-hoan5--lah.¡¨ Jit8-seng na2-chhiuN7 chiaN5 kam2-khai3: ¡§TaN chu7 se3-han3 ka7 liap8 toa7, oat--leh oan-na2 chiuN7-siap--a, na7 mai3 Sin-thiam keo3-sin--khi3, kin-a2-jit8 A-eng ma7 boe7 koe3-tit chiah kan-khou2. Sui-jian5 si7 mia7...., lan2 ma7 bo5-ai3 khoaN3 i chit8-e5 bin7 ng3-tng3 ng3-tng3. Siong7-chhiaN2 A-eng chai7-lai5 to7 lang5-lang5 ho2, lang5-lang5 o-lo2, kap lang5 u7 kong2 u7 chhio3. I chin chai sou2 cho3 e5 tai7-chi3, lan2 bian2 ka7 khoa3-sim--lah.¡¨ ¡§Li2 kan-taN e7-hiau2 kiaN5 bio7-si7 nia5, taN li2 chai chit8-e7 siaN2. A-eng ke chiok gau5 chng li2 chai--bo5? Ke hak kui2-lo7 nia2 saN li2 chai--bo5? Bin7 ke joa7 chhun--leh li2 chai--bo5? Si7 an2-choaN2 sim-hoe hiah khui....?¡¨
